"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:01:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>2019-12-27</strong> <br />\n新一年將至，上任一年的港大校長張翔於新出版的港大年報，於校長專欄發表題為《Cultivating Our Potential》（培育我們的潛力），提到近月的反修例社會運動，對港大是一個考驗，強調學生的安全是校方優先的考量，會盡所能提供協助、支援。張又提到，學校上學年推出了新獎學金、研究計畫，料未來將招募200名學者，並計劃全球招募50名頂尖學者，<strong>期望帶領港大再創高峰</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www4.hku.hk/pubunit/review/ebook_Review2019/2-3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww4.hku.hk%2Fpubunit%2Freview%2Febook_Review2019%2F2-3%2F&d=t9lvrop9ljT%2F%2Fon6qZ%2B%2FxpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=4e14e3d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www4.hku.hk/pubunit/review/ebook_Review2019/2-3/</a>"},{"pid":"78bb3e19b88c116d45bb4806d7c9c3e006f2f5b7","tid":2271710,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"有支那大學排咁高，已經覺得個排位好流，<br />\n不過黨大算鳩數，話之佢排包尾，個名己被黨搞到臭"},{"pid":"dec987abc471e704c7573bc96979f69e8bf5d5bd","tid":2271710,"uid":311184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T18:41:55.000Z","msg":"吾城冇上榜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁過LSE喎"},{"pid":"ccaafb9f638c7b83dda6f69a9d774769c7f5b001","tid":2271710,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa41dfa6c252ac9d2c9e20972f82118a667490c","tid":2271710,"uid":167289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T16:52:08.000Z","msg":"臺大都有40"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"台灣投俾自己？"},{"pid":"2bf3d7031101d89efafb53072ead28e0d54e0b8d","tid":2271710,"uid":345728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T19:47:07.000Z","msg":"點解佢官網啲data同呢篇嘢唔consistent？<br />\n篇野係自己作㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42143d8e0b2f844ca038ebcded01f9e820ca346e","tid":2271710,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T19:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg